ANS- A code environment is a standalone and self-contained environment to run Python. Each code environment has its own set of packages.

There are mainly 3 types of environments:

> Text Editors (sublime,notepad,atom)
> Full IDEs (spyder, pycharm)
> Notebook Environment (Jupyter notebook)
